    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534840/extras/e31a22c9e93aea6a62f8a19c1c081298.poster.avif?t=1766446048\" width=616 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534840/extras/e31a22c9e93aea6a62f8a19c1c081298.webm?t=1766446048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534840/extras/e31a22c9e93aea6a62f8a19c1c081298.mp4?t=1766446048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《光明破坏者》是《光明》系列的全新作品，首次以全3D形式呈现这款开放世界肉鸽游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以独自或与好友一同踏入「繁茂之境」，探索开放世界，打造专属流派，击溃敌人，挑战「冠卫」与「深渊之王」！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534840/extras/3aa674dde109a6493a6761ff24acd8a5.avif?t=1766446048\" width=616 height=75 /></span> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择你的「破坏者」与「僚机」配置，打造独特流派与战斗风格。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可单人游戏或在线合作，闯荡「繁茂之境」。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在紧张刺激的第三人称战斗中，与成群的敌人和强大的Boss激战。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过提升「繁茂之境」的难度来考验你的「破坏者」技能——挑战越大，奖励越丰厚！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534840/extras/6bb65a7f49b248187af0021a12860aab.poster.avif?t=1766446048\" width=616 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534840/extras/6bb65a7f49b248187af0021a12860aab.webm?t=1766446048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534840/extras/6bb65a7f49b248187af0021a12860aab.mp4?t=1766446048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534840/extras/963911b92a2246ceb7684aec93c23477.avif?t=1766446048\" width=616 height=75 /></span> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >世界崩坏，谜团重重，残暴敌人横行，等你深入每一个由全3D构建的区域展开探索。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >广阔而不断变化的世界等待探索，包含大规模开放生态区与深邃迷宫。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用丰富的移动能力——墙面冲刺、悬浮滑板、滑翔翼等自由穿梭各种地形。  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一轮冒险都是全新的体验——角色只有一次生命，死亡后世界将重置，开启全新探索内容。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534840/extras/1abbc27cdf882c17343a8a047d7f1527.poster.avif?t=1766446048\" width=616 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534840/extras/1abbc27cdf882c17343a8a047d7f1527.webm?t=1766446048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534840/extras/1abbc27cdf882c17343a8a047d7f1527.mp4?t=1766446048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534840/extras/186764dfe2f0215fab6dadc3659f31f8.avif?t=1766446048\" width=616 height=75 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从「冠卫」的记忆碎片中逐步揭开「繁茂之境」的神秘面纱。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现并解锁大量武器、道具与强化内容，完成任务还能获得更多奖励，进而强化你的「破坏者」与「繁茂之境」。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将收集到的资源带回定居点并解锁永久升级，这些强化将在你后续的游玩中持续生效。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过详尽的教学系统，深入了解游戏机制，从基础操作到高阶战斗技巧一应俱全。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534840/extras/d7781261e1f9b8f9ceec22eca40acb74.poster.avif?t=1766446048\" width=616 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534840/extras/d7781261e1f9b8f9ceec22eca40acb74.webm?t=1766446048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534840/extras/d7781261e1f9b8f9ceec22eca40acb74.mp4?t=1766446048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p>",
